{"tid":2096642,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人美心善！金賽綸、韓昇延、孔升妍、TWICE定延等為遺棄犬做義工服務","createTime":"2020-07-06T09:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T12:06:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1a8d59ac20bd19bcd57e322e08c002e6f00898","tid":2096642,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"【多圖】孔升妍是這個活動的常客，妹妹定延也經常跟著參加~<br />\n<br />\n在5日上午，Blue Angel志願團的第24期義工服務活動，在京畿道安城市的一家遺棄動物保護所舉行。<br />\n<br />\n獸醫等各行各業人士自發參與，這次有演員20人、超模團體11人、YG娛樂社會貢獻組33人、模特14人、歌手3人、諧星及其他5人等。由組織帶領或以個人身份參與，有些是藝人的熟人，都奉獻出時間參與這項不定期愛心活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/128136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F128136&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=ea3c416d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/128136</a>"},{"pid":"109d6fd53c2707dcdec284bef050847d73cb998d","tid":2096642,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c83c67ed8cff699f040c78dc0ab613e5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-07-05/128136-853841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c83c67ed8cff699f040c78dc0ab613e5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-07-05%2F128136-853841.jpg&h=691f0bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1aaf36c123446159dda866c4ffb3dc7e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-07-05/128136-853843.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1aaf36c123446159dda866c4ffb3dc7e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-07-05%2F128136-853843.jpg&h=b07fcc6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0f18afbbd3e30ed72b4b96238fa31a3dd328d0c","tid":2096642,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_df22